{"tid":1536232,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"要諗定點攞42C 巴士CCTV 片","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:47:43.000Z","uid":108902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b89a9707a91a6861fd2c46e6171e58cc2825a2","tid":1536232,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:08:36.000Z","msg":"車牌TA7682 <br />\n攞定cctv 保障自己<br />\n<br />\n1）狗隻可能濫搜乘客，非法禁錮<br />\n2）頭先有影到白狗扯口罩dum 身份証<br />\n3）可能又老屈<br />\n<br />\n車牌來源<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vHvoRLN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvHvoRLN.jpg&h=11963ebe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7ec94857d86dcb9e6be0c98811acfb01f8d6022","tid":1536232,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4e7bef9c89f109dbc0f0b3921657a6647d0f0e55","tid":1536232,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:09:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d065b85edfa69f579e6cfa796b7c16060876282","tid":1536232,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5b1b83ec183974d52263616b10e64ff9efd2f8f","tid":1536232,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a44892c0927f8ce1a206c1aa60c53b2a8e99ecf6","tid":1536232,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"其實有幾個手足"},{"pid":"59ec972bfcb2e27bd7a1df794a69249a395937a7","tid":1536232,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0180e898ca079bcd853e5400bf1b5f23d95698d6","tid":1536232,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:11:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d6624b506de321d6b45975887e3490d08f9b1172","tid":1536232,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f7f71f116efab83eef9a3ee7b89005a968351716","tid":1536232,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07021696dcbe3d39efc450a44c434f79e8ca4d0b","tid":1536232,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Renq43y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRenq43y.jpg&h=bb73b46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2FTuve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2FTuve.jpg